<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id902998c9-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s2799aa–2"><num value="2799aa–2">§ 2799aa–2.</num><heading> “Nuclear explosive device” defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in this subchapter, the term “nuclear explosive device” has the meaning given that term in <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s6305/4">section 6305(4) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id902998ca-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/629">Pub. L. 90–629</ref>, ch. 10, § 103, as added <ref href="/us/pl/103/236/tVIII/s826/a">Pub. L. 103–236, title VIII, § 826(a)</ref>, <date date="1994-04-30">Apr. 30, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/519">108 Stat. 519</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id902998cb-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id902998cc-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id902998cd-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective 60 days after <date date="1994-04-30">Apr. 30, 1994</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/103/236/s831">section 831 of Pub. L. 103–236</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s6301">section 6301 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
